            <title>[HADOOP-9964] O.A.H.U.ReflectionUtils.printThreadInfo() is not thread-safe which cause TestHttpServer pending 10 minutes or longer.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-9964</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The printThreadInfo() in ReflectionUtils is not thread-safe which cause two or more threads calling this method from StackServlet to deadlock. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
